<consum><title>Consumables</title>
<para>Chapter 1 describes, in detail, the theory of operation and
a functional description of the system and subsystems.<brk>Chapter
2 contains special tools, test equipment, and consumable materials.<brk>Chapter
3 contains system peculiar maintenance that does not lend itself to
Job Guide format.</para>
